author: The Linux Foundation
description:
What a week for open source.
We saw a huge PyTorch upgrade, a strong signal for Wasm adoption, and new security benchmarks that reinforce confidence in OSS infrastructure. Also: one of the fastest-growing forks in recent memory just turned one and more support for electric vehicles.

We break it all down in just 60 seconds. Watch the latest LF Quick Hits and catch up fast.

#OpenSource #LinuxFoundation #AI #CyberSecurity #DevTools
title: Open Source Breakthroughs This Week: PyTorch, Wasm, Security & More
